WEBVTT

00:00.368 --> 00:01.435
Previously on "Heartland"...

00:01.468 --> 00:03.037
What's going on?

00:03.071 --> 00:04.933
- Divorce.
- What do you mean divorce?

00:04.953 --> 00:07.011
We will be there for you,
no matter what.

00:07.031 --> 00:08.609
No you won't! Because if you
wanted to be there for me,

00:08.643 --> 00:10.043
then you wouldn't be doing this!

00:10.077 --> 00:11.578
Are you in love?

00:11.613 --> 00:12.780
No, I barely speak to her.

00:12.814 --> 00:14.448
I mean with Casey.

00:16.796 --> 00:20.354
Come on, we both know Caleb's not
gonna come up with the cash in time,

00:20.388 --> 00:22.122
so pack up your stuff
and get out.

00:22.156 --> 00:24.035
- don't do this.
- Oh, I'm just getting started.

00:24.055 --> 00:25.391
Ungh!

00:25.426 --> 00:27.560
Oh!

00:27.594 --> 00:29.963
- Get your hands off me!
- I've got you now.

00:29.997 --> 00:32.476
Ty, what's going on?
Where were you...?

00:34.880 --> 00:37.067
I think I might be
in trouble, Amy.

00:39.000 --> 00:45.074
